sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as browser
    participant W as web server
    participant C as controller

    B->>W: login (username + password)
    W->>C: POST /api/v1/auth/login
    C-->>W: user_id + scopes
    W-->>B: session cookie

    B->>W: GET /nodes
    Note over W,C: request carries Authorization Bearer system-api-key AND X-On-Behalf-Of user
    W->>C: GET /api/v1/nodes
    Note over C: handler runs with effective_principal = user
    C-->>W: response (user-scoped)
    W-->>B: HTML (composed)
